description: Remotely browse and edit any Azure Repos
config.autoFetch.enabled: Specifies whether to periodically fetch from the upstream repository
config.autoFetch.interval: Specifies the interval, in seconds, to periodically fetch from the upstream repository
config.logLevel.markdownDeprecationMessa: This setting is deprecated. You can instead set the log level using the `Developer: Set Log Level` command.
config.lfs.read.enabled: Controls whether to resolve files tracked via Git LFS from Azure Repos' LFS server
config.lfs.write.enabled: Controls whether to commit files tracked via Git LFS to Azure Repos' LFS server
